103
00:07:43,771 --> 00:07:44,971
What are you doing?

104
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,120
Xiao Che, you are crazy!

105
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,000
I am crazy!

106
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,200
But I cannot compare to you!

107
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,760
What is this?

108
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,840
Since you've already seen it,

109
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,160
